      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just the funding tho. it feels like i've wasted my entire youth on a dead end. even if i started over, who would i even be? i don't have anyone left to turn to and i'm just so drained. i honestly just want to sleep and never have to deal with this pressure or this failure ever again. i just want everything to stop.",
