      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The noise in your head is a real and painful thing to carry, and the desire for quiet is a very understandable response to such intense pressure. But that desire for peace can be found in letting go of the struggle, not in letting go of yourself. Please reach out to a crisis line right now; they are trained to listen to this exact feeling and help you find a different kind of quiet. Your life is worth fighting for, even when it feels impossible.",
      "source": "target",
